{"tid":1850902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸專家李蘭娟：武漢肺炎病毒會在人和寵物間傳播，康復患者難二次感染","createTime":"2020-01-29T19:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T00:44:36.000Z","uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"713e3f98419b162fd81417d9ad7f9e8c185cf342","tid":1850902,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:15:33.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎：病毒會在人和寵物間傳播 康復患者難二次感染<br />\n2020年01月30日 02:38<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/photo/bkn-20200130023847365-0130_00952_001_01p.jpg?20200130030729\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200130023847365-0130_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20200130030729&h=264e52ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李蘭娟指病毒會在人和寵物間傳播。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎持續肆虐內地，引起全國市民關注。內地官媒周四（29日）採訪到身在浙江的中國工程院院士、傳染病學家、國家衞健委高級別專家組成員李蘭娟。她表示新型冠狀病毒可以在哺乳類動物間傳播，所以如果寵物在外感染病毒，有可能傳染給飼主及其他人，需加強防備。<br />\n<br />\n李蘭娟指，新型冠狀病毒會在所有哺乳類動物之間傳播，包括寵物，她呼籲寵物飼主要加強對寵物的管理，如果寵物在外，接觸了武漢肺炎病人，就需要進行有關監控；另外，她表示康復的武漢肺炎患者，會產生一種抗體，一般情況不會被二次感染。<br />\n<br />\n李蘭娟接受採訪時，又回應了周四錄得的確診武漢肺炎人數，已經超過2003年沙士（SARS）爆發時的確診人數，而且數字仍在不斷攀升。李蘭娟指現時的檢測能力和水準遠高於當年，各地社區、街道、醫院，設備都有明顯改進，能有效發現受感染的患者，故不能作比較。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/bkn-20200130023847365-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fbkn-20200130023847365-0130_00952_001.html&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=01bf1dcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/bkn-20200130023847365-0130_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c45e23b6343ffefda15240a4711e6e5db1137484","tid":1850902,"uid":199957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:19:13.000Z","msg":"佢咁講 即係話SARS果陣有隱瞞啦?"},{"pid":"5626f59f3056f1b3609c48e28ff0b97fe4f632c9","tid":1850902,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\nbtw p牌求推一推... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥 借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"3ecd3b89fb996b7b680b5440b64dd54922eeb6d4","tid":1850902,"uid":85586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:21:32.000Z","msg":"之前強制斬大狗<br />\n𠵱家想斬埋其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75076ba3e66da838ad1192407fcba89b18f6c9f","tid":1850902,"uid":226955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:22:09.000Z","msg":"首先你要過咗第一次感染之後唔死先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5054584207a76732f908c9fd96969182f2ea814a","tid":1850902,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c45e23b6343ffefda15240a4711e6e5db1137484","tid":1850902,"uid":199957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:19:13.000Z","msg":"佢咁講 即係話SARS果陣有隱瞞啦?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:26:18.000Z","msg":"最尾句故不能作比較真係戴曬頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460bd381e5912df6b93270897a0052596cdbac1e","tid":1850902,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f75076ba3e66da838ad1192407fcba89b18f6c9f","tid":1850902,"uid":226955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:22:09.000Z","msg":"首先你要過咗第一次感染之後唔死先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:27:50.000Z","msg":"病毒基因唔同左嘅話有抗體都未必有用"},{"pid":"91591bd074d2952b41925f3f805d253c298a6fdd","tid":1850902,"uid":1999